login from vm in same subnet(id_rsa will allog to login inside node as we have used --generate-ssh during cluster creation):


    
scp id_rsa user123@vm.public.ip:~

    
ssh user123@vm.publicip

    
ssh -i id_rsa azureuser@10.12.42.4


